# How to Customize Images and Text

## üìù Changing Text Content

### 1. Welcome Screen Text
**File:** `src/components/WelcomeScreen.tsx`
- **Line 75-76:** Change "Hello" and "KuchuPuchu" to your desired names
```tsx
<h1 className="text-8xl...">Hello</h1>
<h2 className="text-4xl...">YourName</h2>
```

### 2. Photo Scene Text
**File:** `src/components/PhotoScene.tsx`
- **Line 310-311:** Change the anniversary message
```tsx
<MainTitle>Here's Another Year Together</MainTitle>
<SubTitle>I LOVE YOUUU</SubTitle>
```

### 3. Particle Scene Text
**File:** `src/components/ParticleScene.tsx`
- **Line 126-133:** Customize the romantic message
```tsx
<h1>Every Moment</h1>
<h2>With You</h2>
<h3>Is Pure Magic ‚ú®</h3>
```

### 4. Cake Scene Text
**File:** `src/components/CakeScene.tsx`
- **Line 377-378:** Change cake message
```tsx
<p>üéÇ I Cooked An Anniversary Cake For You! üéÇ</p>
<p>Make a wish and cut the cake bb...</p>
```

### 5. Page Title
**File:** `index.html`
- **Line 6:** Change the browser tab title
```html
<title>Happy Anniversary YourName ‚ù§Ô∏è</title>
```

## üñºÔ∏è Changing Images

### 1. Welcome Screen GIF
**File:** `src/components/WelcomeScreen.tsx`
- **Step 1:** Add your GIF to `src/imgs/` folder
- **Step 2:** Update import on line 3:
```tsx
import YourGif from '../imgs/your-gif-name.gif'
```
- **Step 3:** Update line 56:
```tsx
src={YourGif}
```

### 2. Couple Photo
**File:** `src/components/PhotoScene.tsx`
- **Step 1:** Add your couple photo to `src/imgs/` folder (recommended: 400x400px or square ratio)
- **Step 2:** Update import on line 4:
```tsx
import CouplePhoto from '../imgs/your-photo.jpg';
```

### 3. Balloon Images (Cake Scene)
**File:** `src/components/CakeScene.tsx`
- **Step 1:** Add balloon images to `src/imgs/` folder
- **Step 2:** Update imports on lines 7-9:
```tsx
import Balloon1 from '../imgs/your-balloon1.png'
import Balloon2 from '../imgs/your-balloon2.png'
import Balloon3 from '../imgs/your-balloon3.png'
```

## üé® Changing Colors

### 1. Main Theme Colors
**File:** `src/components/WelcomeScreen.tsx` (and other components)
- Find color classes like `text-pink-600`, `bg-purple-50`
- Replace with your preferred Tailwind colors:
  - `text-blue-600` for blue text
  - `text-green-600` for green text
  - `bg-yellow-50` for light yellow background

### 2. Cake Colors
**File:** `src/components/CakeScene.tsx`
- **Lines 21-24:** Change cake color constants
```tsx
const vanilla = '#your-color';
const chocolate = '#your-color';
const candleColor = '#your-color';
```

## üìÅ Image File Requirements

- **Supported formats:** .jpg, .jpeg, .png, .gif
- **Welcome GIF:** Any size (will be auto-resized)
- **Couple Photo:** Square ratio recommended (400x400px ideal)
- **Balloons:** PNG with transparent background works best
- **File naming:** Use simple names without spaces (use-dashes-or_underscores)

## üîß Advanced Customizations

### Adding New Scenes
1. Create new component in `src/components/`
2. Add to scenes array in `src/App.tsx`
3. Follow existing component patterns

### Changing Animation Timing
- Look for `setTimeout` and `gsap.timeline` in component files
- Adjust duration values (in milliseconds for setTimeout, seconds for GSAP)

### Custom Styling
- Most components use Tailwind CSS classes
- Some use styled-components (CakeScene, PhotoScene)
- Modify className attributes or styled component definitions

## ‚ö†Ô∏è Important Notes

1. **Always backup your original files** before making changes
2. **Test changes locally** using `npm run dev` before hosting
3. **Image file paths are case-sensitive** on hosting platforms
4. **Keep image files under 5MB** for better loading performance
5. **After making changes, restart the dev server** (Ctrl+C then `npm run dev`)

## üêõ Common Issues

- **Images not showing:** Check file path and extension spelling
- **Text not updating:** Clear browser cache (Ctrl+F5)
- **Site not loading:** Check terminal for error messages
- **Build errors:** Make sure all imported files exist

---

**Need help?** Contact me with screenshots of any errors you encounter!
